    "AIGC demonstrates strong capabilities in video content creation and processing and has been widely used for generating trailers and promotional videos (Ren, 2024; Loeschcke et al., 2022).",
    "Building on this foundation, AIGC can play an even larger role.",
    "For example, AIGC's powerful content generation capabilities can be fully utilized to create diverse traffic safety education materials.",
    "Through AIGC, vivid videos can be produced that use real cases and impactful visuals to illustrate the dangers of traffic accidents, raising public awareness.",
